{"tid":1496100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如喺機場「流水式集會」","createTime":"2019-08-22T10:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T09:20:55.000Z","uid":191462,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"53052d5b744ca6b9bbdb8cf9f4422e13385836b1","tid":1496100,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r8vRR7s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr8vRR7s.jpg&h=3d0ed09e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然機管局劃出嘅集會區咁細<br />\n仲細過維園<br />\n太多人迫埋一齊 好似唔係咁好<br />\n<br />\n咁不如我哋學民陣咁搞「流水式集會」<br />\n喺集會區集會咗一陣嘅人 <br />\n就讓俾其他想集會嘅人進入<br />\n咁當然走咗嘅人再想入多次嚟就悉隨尊便啦<br />\n<br />\n同埋喺圖中白色區域時<br />\n大家就要自律確保有一定流動性<br />\n<br />\nFor example: 左入右出<br />\n<br />\n咁先唔會變做非法集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3381f81652a5b0707d038cd82ee588f0a7a101f5","tid":1496100,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:59:36.000Z","msg":"問題依家入唔入到去都成問題"},{"pid":"7ac675ac640487e6a34593276c639997cfad447a","tid":1496100,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3381f81652a5b0707d038cd82ee588f0a7a101f5","tid":1496100,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:59:36.000Z","msg":"問題依家入唔入到去都成問題"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:01:37.000Z","msg":"禁制令到23/8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697720f55ee87d34bc93363c175205d6327bbedc","tid":1496100,"uid":108347,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3381f81652a5b0707d038cd82ee588f0a7a101f5","tid":1496100,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:59:36.000Z","msg":"問題依家入唔入到去都成問題"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T11:01:57.000Z","msg":"點解會入唔到? 佢check登機證你未照排隊，你一樣係塞死哂個機場，你有三幾萬人排隊佢已經收撚哂皮，佢停交通仲爽，目的一樣達到"},{"pid":"6d7053170e3d3925c0f22ea6579f9fc872794056","tid":1496100,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor